<ol type="a">
<li><p>If <m>U\  = \ \{ 1,\ 2,\ 3,\ 4,\ 5,\ 6,\ 7\}</m> and <m>A\  = \ \{ 2,\ 4,\ 6\}</m>, then a Venn diagram representation of these two sets looks like the following.</p></li>
</ol>

